spell_list.description: Inflicts minor damage to the targets around the troubador. For each target struck, the troubador gains increased damage to the encounter for a single strike. This effect increments up to 24 times. A small amount of power will be restored with this attack. Higher ranks lower the base reuse time.
spell_list.description_pvp: Inflicts minor damage to the targets around the troubador. For each target struck, the troubador gains increased damage to the encounter for a single strike. This effect increments up to 24 times. A small amount of power will be restored with this attack. Higher ranks lower the base reuse time.

effect_list.description: Inflicts 2 - 4 magic damage on targets in Area of Effect
Applies Energetic Reverberation.  Lasts for 30.0 seconds.
On any combat or spell hit this spell will cast Energetic Reverberation on target of attack.
Inflicts 5 - 9 magic damage on target encounter
Increases power of group members (AE) by 1
